article_title: The New Economy: Many workers booting careers amid economic 'Uberization'
article_text:
News Herald Reporter Follow @@PCNHCollinB By COLLIN BREAUX News Herald Reporter

Posted Nov. 23, 2015 at 6:15 AM

Updated Jan 13, 2016 at 8:39 AM

article_metadata.description: With the workforce changing, The News Herald is taking a look at some of the factors at play in a three-part series that began Sunday. Part one examined minimum wage and the national Fight for 15 campaign, and part two explored potential changes in federal overtime rules.
article_metadata.author: COLLIN BREAUX
